msgctxt "settings"
msgid "Chat"
msgstr "Xat"

msgctxt "settings"
msgid ""
"Chat (via our Duck.ai service) lets you have anonymous conversations with 3rd-"
"party AI chat models, which supports models from OpenAI, Anthropic, and more. "
"Turning this setting off will hide Chat buttons and links on DuckDuckGo "
"Search. However, you can still access Chat when this setting is off by "
"visiting %shttps://duck.ai%s directly."
msgstr ""
"El xat (a través del nostre servei Duck.ai) us permet tenir converses anònimes "
"amb models de xat d'IA de tercers, que suporta models d'OpenAI, Anthropic, i "
"més. En activar aquesta opció, s'ocultaran els botons del xat i els enllaços a "
"la cerca del DuckDuckGo. No obstant això, encara podeu accedir al xat quan "
"aquesta configuració estigui desactivada visitant %shttps://duck.ai%s "
"directament."

