msgctxt "settings"
msgid ""
"Duck.ai lets you have anonymous conversations with 3rd-party AI chat models, "
"including models from OpenAI, Anthropic, and others. Turning this setting off "
"will hide Duck.ai buttons and links on DuckDuckGo Search. However, you can "
"still access Duck.ai when this setting is off by visiting %shttps://duck.ai%s "
"directly."
msgstr ""
"El Duck.ai us permet tenir converses anònimes amb models de xat d'IA de "
"tercers, inclosos models d'OpenAI, Anthropic i altres. En activar aquesta "
"opció, s'ocultaran els botons i enllaços del Duck.ai a la cerca de DuckDuckGo. "
"No obstant això, encara podeu accedir al Duck.ai quan aquesta configuració "
"estigui desactivada visitant %shttps://duck.ai%s directament."

