msgctxt "settings"
msgid ""
"Search Assist anonymously generates answers for search queries. To do this, it "
"scans the web for relevant content and then uses AI to generate a brief "
"answer. You can choose how often you want it to appear: Never, On-demand (only "
"when Assist is clicked), Sometimes (when highly relevant), or Often (on a wide "
"range of searches). For now, Search Assist is only available in a subset of "
"English speaking regions."
msgstr ""
"El Search Assist genera de manera anònima respostes per a les consultes de "
"cerca. Per fer-ho, escaneja el web per obtenir contingut rellevant i després "
"utilitza la IA per generar una resposta breu. Podeu triar amb quina freqüència "
"voleu que aparegui: Mai, sota demanda (només quan es fa clic a l'Assist), De "
"vegades (quan és molt rellevant), o Sovint (en una àmplia gamma de cerques). "
"De moment, Search Assist només està disponible en un subconjunt de regions de "
"parla anglesa."

#. Error message for the duckassist instant answer (based on generative AI)
#. when the answer is not found and the answer is unsourced or with no sources
msgid ""
"Search Assist couldn't find enough reliable information to generate an answer "
"for this question. Try another search."
msgstr ""
"El Search Assist no ha pogut trobar prou informació fiable per a generar una "
"resposta per a aquesta pregunta. Proveu amb una altra cerca."

#. First paragraph of a section inviting users to learn more about the Assist
#. instant answer (based on generative AI)
msgid ""
"Search Assist is an optional feature that anonymously generates answers for "
"search queries. To do this, it %sscans the web%s for relevant content and then "
"uses AI to generate a brief answer based on information found."
msgstr ""
"El Search Assist és una característica opcional que genera de manera anònima "
"respostes per a les consultes de cerca. Per fer-ho, %sescaneja el web%s per a "
"contingut rellevant i després utilitza la IA per generar una resposta breu "
"basada en la informació trobada."

