msgid ""
"The model provider deletes any data associated with this chat within 30 days."
msgstr ""
"El proveïdor del model suprimeix qualsevol dada associada amb aquest xat en un "
"termini de 30 dies."

#. Description explaining that the AI model provider does not store any chat
#. data on their servers.
msgctxt "Privacy claim description in Duck.ai chat"
msgid ""
"The model provider does not save this chat or any associated data on their "
"servers."
msgstr ""
"El proveïdor del model no guarda aquest xat ni cap dada associada als seus "
"servidors."

