#. immediately reloading the page.
msgctxt "noresults"
msgid ""
"There was still an error displaying the search results. Please wait a few "
"minutes before you try again."
msgstr ""
"Encara hi ha hagut un error en mostrar els resultats de la cerca. Espereu uns "
"minuts abans de tornar-ho a provar."

#. Error message for explore more questions when a retryable error occurs
#. (timeout, network)
msgid "There's been an issue loading this answer. Please try again."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha hagut un problema en carregar aquesta resposta. Torneu-ho a provar."

#. Instant Answer Tab Name
